{
  "texts": [
    "This highlights the need to combine the use of ChatGPT with traditional methods to maximize benefits in research education.",
    "D. General Interpretation of the ResultsUnlike previous studies that have focused on the general capabilities of ChatGPT in educational settings, this study offers a more specific analysis of its impact on the development of research competencies in regular basic education students.",
    "This methodological difference allows for a deeper exploration of how artificial intelligence can be integrated into the teaching-learning process of research at an educational level where critical skills are often in their early stages of development.The results show that, in terms of coherence, precision, and originality, the experimental group outperformed the control group.",
    "This finding suggests that ChatGPT has a positive effect on the structure and clarity of thought in the research domain, which differs from previous studies that found AI tools to be more useful in simpler or repetitive tasks.",
    "Here, ChatGPT not only supports content generation but also facilitates logical organization of ideas and promotes the generation of novel insights."
  ]
}